In re Resignation of Miller.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Miller (1992), 64 Ohio St.3d 1205.]

(No. 92-1082 Submitted June 17, 1992 Decided June 24, 1992.)

The resignation of Otto Miller III as an attorney, Registration No. 0003636, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
